From: Logan Gunthorpe <logang@deltatee.com>
Date: Wed, 12 Aug 2020 17:24:44 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] nvme: Use spin_lock_irq() when taking the ctrl->lock
Git-commit: ecbcdf0c81265f7f780b588eed77fa933fd79f68
Patch-mainline: v5.9-rc3
References: jsc#SLE-15608

